author: COMSOL
description: In this example, the transient response of a shallow foundation resting on an unsaturated soil stratum is investigated. The changes in pore suction due to water infiltration or evaporation is investigated using the Extended Barcelona Basic soil model. The results show the deformation of the clay stratum due to footing pressure and changes in pore suction.
